INSTALAR PYTHON
http://www.python.org/download/releases/2.6.5/

DISTRIBUTE

http://pypi.python.org/packages/source/d/distribute/distribute-0.6.14.tar.gz
$ tar zxf distribute-0.6.14.tar.gz
$ cd distribute-0.6.14
$ sudo python setup.py install


PIP

$ sudo easy_install pip

VIRTUALENV

$ sudo pip install virtualenv

CREACION ENTORNO JAPOS

virtualenv --distribute --no-site-packages japos26
cd japos26/
source bin/activate

DJANGO
pip install django